<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/arts-council-england> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Arts Council England champions, develops and invests in artistic and cultural experiences to enrich people’s lives. It supports a range of activities across the arts, museums and libraries - from theatre to digital art - reading to dance, music to literature, and crafts to collections. Arts Council England is an executive non-departmental public body, sponsored by the Department for Culture, Media and Sport ."@en .
